{"tid":1048573,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"覺得中年港女普遍難頂","createTime":"2019-03-05T18:01:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-05T18:11:30.000Z","uid":216760,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"ea05952333b0467d7b71d8340e486280d31e9ce8","tid":1048573,"uid":216760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T18:01:15.000Z","msg":"今日做左啲事俾個中年港女大大聲質問，嘗試同佢爭辯但輸晒，唯有死死地氣，西住面順中年港女意思去做。<br />\n<br />\n好心路人主動話幫忙，仲講左兩次，我當時因為俾人鬧完情緒未tune好，所以只係黑口黑面同好心路人講: 唔洗啦 ，唔該~ <br />\n<br />\n事後心情平伏返，好想同好心人講聲多謝，人間有愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n希望自己轉數快啲，以後面對呢啲事可以處理得好啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b10021268594ec78ab684ab516034c964367322","tid":1048573,"uid":90820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T18:03:37.000Z","msg":"個標題講中年閪女人<br />\n但內文又得引入係關佢事<br />\n中間就多謝好心人<br />\n結尾就問點樣轉數快啲<br />\n個post到底想講乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f2e29df5af86fc3c20cdc905ae522597ff1ce78","tid":1048573,"uid":51171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T18:06:39.000Z","msg":"『黑口黑面同路人講：唔洗喇唔該』"},{"pid":"a4ada2cbccf6c4f017b4057cc1e179d1d5c17a78","tid":1048573,"uid":216760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7b10021268594ec78ab684ab516034c964367322","tid":1048573,"uid":90820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T18:03:37.000Z","msg":"個標題講中年閪女人<br />\n但內文又得引入係關佢事<br />\n中間就多謝好心人<br />\n結尾就問點樣轉數快啲<br />\n個post到底想講乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T18:09:30.000Z","msg":"其實主要係想多謝好心人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n前面係交代背景，後面係個人反思(例如轉數夠快就會當下即刻處理好心情，好好多謝路人甲)，標題係頭先無諗清楚錯重點"},{"pid":"7effc474f19135a8e057b4f17f1c2c6ad95d6d5a","tid":1048573,"uid":216760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"